00:31:00,592 --> 00:31:04,084
<i>*And I know you won't let me down *</i>

401
00:31:04,162 --> 00:31:06,096
Yoo-hoo, Michael.

402
00:31:06,164 --> 00:31:08,598
<i>* 'Cause I'm already **</i>
Michael.

403
00:31:10,501 --> 00:31:12,366
Hello, Michael.

404
00:31:12,437 --> 00:31:14,564
[Beeps]

405
00:31:14,639 --> 00:31:17,472
[Tires Squealing]

406
00:31:17,542 --> 00:31:21,945
<i>* Open your eyes</i>
