416
00:31:45,670 --> 00:31:48,332
<i>[Siren Whirring]</i>

417
00:31:48,406 --> 00:31:50,567
[Tires Squealing]

418
00:31:50,642 --> 00:31:52,473
<i>* Why not think about *</i>

419
00:31:52,543 --> 00:31:54,477
[Siren Whirring]

420
00:31:54,545 --> 00:31:56,410
<i>How can he be asleep</i>
<i>and drive like that?</i>

421
00:31:56,481 --> 00:31:59,245
<i>- **</i> [Continues]
- [KITT Whispers]
Michael.

422
00:32:00,652 --> 00:32:03,849
- Michael.
<i>- **[Stops]</i>

423
00:32:03,922 --> 00:32:06,584
[Horn Honking]

424
00:32:06,658 --> 00:32:08,649
Hey! Hey!

425
00:32:08,726 --> 00:32:11,422
- [Honking Continues]
- Michael.

426
00:32:11,496 --> 00:32:13,930
Hey!

427
00:32:13,998 --> 00:32:16,592
Pull back.

428
00:32:16,668 --> 00:32:18,795
What the...

429
00:32:18,870 --> 00:32:20,838
