you display a slight kink in your neck...

435
00:32:39,457 --> 00:32:42,392
since you were driving
with your head against the window.

436
00:32:43,861 --> 00:32:46,853
- I said out!
- Why didn't you warn me?

437
00:32:46,931 --> 00:32:48,956
You told me to keep quiet.

438
00:32:49,033 --> 00:32:52,696
Who's he talkin' to?
Nobody.
This boy's a hard-core alkie.

439
00:32:52,770 --> 00:32:55,170
Did you hear me?

440
00:32:55,239 --> 00:32:59,005
I said get out
if you don't wanna
spend the night in jail.

441
00:32:59,077 --> 00:33:01,739
That's better.
Now come on out.
Get the balloon out, Deke.

442
00:33:01,813 --> 00:33:03,747
<i>[Loudly]</i>
<i>I'm sorry, Officer.</i>

443
00:33:03,815 --> 00:33:07,751
