or a little slower.

444
00:33:07,819 --> 00:33:10,515
<i>I haven't gotten</i>
<i>lipreading down yet.</i>

445
00:33:10,588 --> 00:33:12,522
You mean you can't hear?

446
00:33:17,195 --> 00:33:20,995
Could you talk a little louder?
Into this ear... here.

447
00:33:21,065 --> 00:33:22,760
You mean you're deaf?

448
00:33:23,968 --> 00:33:27,028
Oh, that explains everything.

449
00:33:27,105 --> 00:33:29,869
I told you he couldn't drive
that smooth if he was drunk.

450
00:33:29,941 --> 00:33:31,932
What?

451
00:33:32,010 --> 00:33:35,036
He said...
Never mind!

452
00:33:35,113 --> 00:33:38,640
Just be on your way.
We're sorry we bothered ya.

453
00:33:38,716 --> 00:33:41,514
Uh, but keep your eye
on the rearview mirror.

454
00:33:41,586 --> 00:33:44,453
We've been flashing ya for miles.

455
00:33:44,522 --> 00:33:47,082
Yes, sir. I'll do that.

