Here you go.
Take your place
with the valley's finest.

735
00:51:41,331 --> 00:51:43,959
Oh, you're a doll.

736
00:51:44,034 --> 00:51:46,594
But I can't find Buddy.
I don't know where that kid's gone.

737
00:51:46,670 --> 00:51:50,629
Don't worry about him.
