Piece of cake.

741
00:52:00,450 --> 00:52:02,816
Our sleek field of cars are revving up.

742
00:52:02,886 --> 00:52:05,411
<i>Getting ready to go.</i>
<i>The starter's in position.</i>

743
00:52:05,489 --> 00:52:07,684
<i>By the way,</i>
<i>we've got a new entry...</i>
<i>Michael Knight,</i>

744
00:52:07,757 --> 00:52:09,725
<i>an independent driver</i>
<i>in a black Trans-Am.</i>

745
00:52:09,793 --> 00:52:11,727
<i>And the race is on.!</i>

746
00:52:11,795 --> 00:52:14,525
<i>Remember, ladies and gentlemen,</i>
<i>this is a figure-eight track,</i>

747
00:52:14,598 --> 00:52:17,658
