<i>Apiece of sheet metal</i>
<i>in a viselike maneuver,</i>

787
00:54:33,770 --> 00:54:35,704
<i>but Knight rocketed</i>
<i>right between 'em...</i>

788
00:54:35,772 --> 00:54:38,104
<i>and averted certain destruction.</i>

