00:54:49,786 --> 00:54:51,447
I don't even know
what those things do.

794
00:54:51,521 --> 00:54:56,117
<i>[Announcer] I'll tell you.</i>
<i>When you're in a race like this, you better</i>
<i>have a good, firm grip on that wheel,</i>

