00:54:56,192 --> 00:54:58,183
<i>because anybody...</i>
<i>Whoa.! Here's a slide-out right now.!</i>

796
00:54:58,261 --> 00:55:00,286
Wow! All right!

797
00:55:00,363 --> 00:55:02,160
<i>[Announcer]</i>
<i>And a spinout by Dolan.</i>

798
00:55:02,232 --> 00:55:04,666
<i>And it appears</i>
<i>that Dolan is stalled over there.</i>

799
00:55:04,734 --> 00:55:07,362
<i>He'd better get that vehicle going fast.</i>
<i>He's a sitting duck.</i>

800
00:55:07,437 --> 00:55:10,565
All right, Buddy.
Just sit tight and don't touch anything.

801
00:55:10,640 --> 00:55:12,835
<i>[Announcer]</i>
<i>A move on our lead car,</i>
<i>driven by Michael Knight,</i>

802
00:55:12,909 --> 00:55:15,139
<i>the daring independent</i>
<i>in that black Trans-Am.</i>

803
00:55:15,211 --> 00:55:18,703
<i>- This wily veteran has the equipment</i>
<i>to catch the Trans-Am.</i>
- [Beeps]

