00:55:37,400 --> 00:55:39,561
<i>as the Caddy gets caught</i>
<i>in the intersection there.</i>

811
00:55:39,636 --> 00:55:42,400
<i>Knight's got trouble</i>
<i>getting around the Caddy,</i>
<i>but he barely made it.</i>

812
00:55:44,107 --> 00:55:46,871
<i>Two more cars</i>
<i>flying over that Cadillac,</i>
<i>our</i> f<i>ield is further reduced.</i>

813
00:55:46,943 --> 00:55:50,743
<i>And now it looks like...</i>
<i>Oh.! Here comes the Lincoln</i>
<i>into the pileup.</i>

814
00:55:50,814 --> 00:55:54,272
[Laughing]
Come to papa. Come to papa.

815
00:56:01,624 --> 00:56:03,524
<i>And now only two are le</i>ft.

816
00:56:03,593 --> 00:56:05,754
Now you're up against number one.

817
00:56:05,829 --> 00:56:09,390
All right, Buddy. You ready?
Ready.

818
00:56:09,466 --> 00:56:11,559
<i>[Michael]</i>
<i>Here we go.</i>

819
00:56:14,804 --> 00:56:17,238
That car's incredible, Tanya.

820
00:56:19,142 --> 00:56:23,272
<i>[Announcer]</i>
<i>A bump in the road</i>
<i>caused the Trans-Am to go airborne.</i>

821
00:56:23,346 --> 00:56:26,076
<i>And that means the only one</i>
<i>who got to the finish line...</i>

822
00:56:26,149 --> 00:56:29,084
We won! We won! We won!

823
00:56:29,152 --> 00:56:32,451
<i>It's Michael Knight.!</i>
<i>As he takes the checkered flag.</i>

824
00:56:32,522 --> 00:56:35,286
<i>The amazing thing,</i>
<i>from our point of vantage,</i>
<i>ladies and gentlemen...</i>

825
00:56:35,358 --> 00:56:37,326
I want to know
all about that young man.

826
00:56:37,394 --> 00:56:39,521
That makes two of us.

827
00:56:39,596 --> 00:56:42,793
<i>A demolition derby</i>
<i>with a car coming out</i>
<i>without a scratch is unheard of.</i>

828
00:56:42,866 --> 00:56:44,800
<i>An absolute miracle.</i>

829
00:56:44,868 --> 00:56:47,735
<i>And Michael Knight,</i>
<i>the young independent from nowhere...</i>

830
00:56:47,804 --> 00:56:51,001
<i>and I mean literally</i>
<i>from nowhere...</i>

831
00:56:51,074 --> 00:56:53,702
Tanya. You saw what I'm selling.

832
00:56:53,777 --> 00:56:56,974
